r2.name: Amber Bradshaw
r2.text: Mr. Buchholz and his employee Ryan came out to our property and put brand new plumbing in our home. The work was quality and super affordable! They are great guys that are super professional and have awesome customer service. Would definitely recommend!

r4.name: Donna Jackson
r4.text: I called in need of my toilet to be repaired. He fit me in same day. He showed up when he said he would. He was very professional. I will definitely be calling him again if I have need. Fair price as well.

r1.name: Terry Smith
r1.text: Excellent service excellent staff that helps you without having to wait for your Hardware needs and McComb Mississippi Handy's Hardware have that old time hardware store feeling when you go there I do recommend Handy's Hardware in the town I might know you Mississippi right next to the railroad tracks

r2.name: Crystal Easley
r2.text: Love this store! Every time I go in I am greeted with a warm welcome and always someone ready to help me find exactly what I need and then bring it to my car if need be. We have shopped here forever and will continue!

r3.name: Michelle Mrs
r3.text: Awesome store , great staff. I never know what my husband sending me to get....but they do and act like it's no biggie that I'm clueless. LoL for that reason alone I'm forever a customer.

r4.name: Tricia Laster
r4.text: The staff is great and helpful.  If you have a project that is out of the norm give them a try.  They'll give you ideas on how to do the project while keeping your budget in mind.

r5.name: Jerrie Cutrer
r5.text: Great small town hardware store. Has hard and easy to find items. Always had someone to help you. Service is excellent!

r1.name: Micah Cotten
r1.text: Called them at 8am they came and pumped the septic tank showed us where they believe the problem to be and was gone by 10:15am very fast and informative on issues. Great job, 2 other places gave us the runaround for 8 days. They had the job done within 2 hours of first contact.

r3.name: Kenneth Martin
r3.text: Mike is the best around! He knows what he is doing, is fairly priced, responds quick and is a real asset to Selma and Dallas County!

r4.name: Maria Craft
r4.text: Very good people. When I initally spoke to the office they said it would take a week but they came later on that day! Customers are their first priority. They get a good rating on responding in a timely manner! They will do the correct work necessary without looking for an easy way around it!

r5.name: Stone Thames
r5.text: Alex and the guys at M&M are great. They really know what they're doing and will get any plumbing need you have done quickly, done well and at a reasonable fee. Highly recommend!

r6.name: Kristy Sistrunk
r6.text: I used M & M for a commercial plumbing issue I had at work and I couldn't be more pleased.  Alex was very professional and made sure the job was well done at a reasonable price.  I will recommend M & M from now on.
